What is Levels?

Levels helps you achieve clarity and control over your health by revealing comprehensive biomarker data and clear guidance toward your goals. With access to blood testing, continuous glucose monitors, and 1-on-1 dietitian support, you can uncover deeper insights into your body. Features like AI-powered food logging, habit tracking, and adaptive insights help translate that data into daily actions that drive measurable improvement.

CONTINUOUS GLUCOSE MONITORING

Real-Time Blood Sugar Insights

LEARN HOW FOODS AFFECT YOU

Find the healthiest diet for you

Levels lets you add continuous glucose monitoring—a small sensor on your upper arm for up to two weeks of real-time data about how your food and lifestyle choices impact your health. Get the latest CGMs sent to your door anytime.

Continuous, convenient data

Wear your CGM while you sleep, shower, swim—you'll forget it's there and it delivers data 24/7

Monitor at your own pace.

Choose a plan that works for you—monthly, quarterly, or one-time to check in on your metabolic health.

Bring your own CGM

Already using one? Sync your data with Levels to unlock deeper health insights.

More than a third of US Adults now have prediabetes,

and most of them don’t even know it. A Continuous Glucose Monitor helps you manage your metabolic health by showing how diet and lifestyle impact your blood sugar in real-time.

What is a Continuous Glucose Monitor?

A CGM is a quarter-sized sensor worn on your upper arm for up to two weeks, providing real-time insights into how food, exercise, and lifestyle impact your blood sugar. It syncs with the Levels app to deliver personalized recommendations and research-backed tips. Designed for daily wear, it stays secure with a performance cover—even during workouts and swimming.
